      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ALTONA BEACH (7) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 16.70 beating Divorce Papers. Got the money at her only try from this box. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. RUSTY ACES (5) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Finished third (17.46) at Casino latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Must be included in calculations. FINLEY BALE (2) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing seventh (23.18) in a P5 at Q Lakeside. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. SON OF BOB (1) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
